#: ../../doc/extra/known_issue.rst:2
msgid "Known Issues"
msgstr "已知问题"

#: ../../doc/extra/known_issue.rst:4
msgid ""
"Some features of this library may not work on some broken compiler or "
"standard library."
msgstr "此库的某些功能可能无法在某些有缺陷的编译器或标准库上正常工作。"

#: ../../doc/extra/known_issue.rst:6
msgid ""
"If you bind an overloaded function using syntax like "
"``static_cast<return_type(*)()>(&func)`` on MSVC, it may crash the compiler."
msgstr ""
"如果您在 MSVC 上使用 ``static_cast<return_type(*)()>(&func)`` 这样的语法绑定"
"重载函数，可能会导致编译器崩溃。"

#: ../../doc/extra/known_issue.rst:7
msgid ""
"The workaround is to write a standalone wrapper function with no "
"overloading, then bind this wrapper using asbind20. You can also try the "
"``overload_cast`` tool."
msgstr ""
"解决方法是编写一个没有重载的独立包装函数，然后使用 asbind20 绑定此包装函数。"
"您也可以尝试使用 ``overload_cast`` 工具。"

#: ../../doc/extra/known_issue.rst:9
msgid ""
"GCC (at least for 14.2) may `not generate machine code of registered "
"template class on a rare occasion <https://gcc.gnu.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?"
"id=119233>`_. If you encounter a linker error like `this example on Compiler "
"Explorer <https://godbolt.org/z/oT9cP1rso>`_ , try to use explicit "
"instantiation for your template class."
msgstr ""
"GCC（至少 14.2 版本）可能 `在极少数情况下不会生成已注册模板类的机器码 "
"<https://gcc.gnu.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=119233>`_。如果您遇到类似 "
"`Compiler Explorer 上的这个示例 <https://godbolt.org/z/oT9cP1rso>`_ 的链接器"
"错误，请尝试为您的模板类使用显式实例化。"

#: ../../doc/extra/known_issue.rst:11
msgid ""
"Older compilers (like GCC 12) may wrongly think some types in asbind20 are "
"dependent types, so you need to add ``template`` disambiguator as a "
"workaround."
msgstr ""
"较旧的编译器（如 GCC 12）可能错误地认为 asbind20 中的某些类型是依赖类型，因此"
"您需要添加 ``template`` 消歧义符作为解决方法。"
